To create a new react+vitejs project with the standard folder structure the below command:

/Users/neerajapradeep/AMAI/scaffold-structure.sh --create app-name auth profile 

Note: Makesure to keep the scaffold-structure.sh file in the root folder where you run this command and give the root folder path 
instead of /Users/neerajapradeep/AMAI/scaffold-structure.sh
And also replace the term app-name with the project folder name accordingly.
